Energy

Summary of who wasted the most energy and who cost the enemy the most energy.
Calculated by adding up Losses (and Stalemates, Defends, Escapes, Interrupts) and Defends, the multiplying the number by 25.
E_Wasted means the member spent X energy on attacks that failed.
E_Stolen means X energy was wasted by the enemy on attacking the member unsuccessfully.
You might want to take a closer look at members with high E_Wasted values and remind them to pick fights they can win!

1 These numbers will be 0 if you are using an API key WITHOUT faction access.

AI summary (BETA)

This is an experimental portion of the report - an overview of the war generated by AI.
When looking at this section, keep that in mind and take the results with a grain of salt.
Before taking any actions that might impact faction members mentioned in this summary, double-check that there are no mistakes or missed key details.

Here is a summary of the provided combat data:

Overall Faction Performance

The faction demonstrates moderate activity with a portion of its members engaging in war hits. There is a mix of positive and negative Net_Scores, suggesting varied individual performances. Some members show good team play through assists, while others exhibit higher energy wastage. Respect and Score values are not indicative of overall faction performance and thus are not focused on in the summary.

Areas for Improvement

  • Reduce energy wasted on failed attacks (E_Wasted).
  • Improve target selection to minimize losses.
  • Increase the number of members actively participating in war hits.

Individual Highlights: Positive

  • RipleyWolf: Highest activity (5.673 hours) and significant number of war hits (46).
  • The_Totem: High war hits (54) despite low activity, indicating efficient engagement.
  • Supreme_: High number of total hits (57) and a good FairFight score (2.19).

Individual Highlights: Negative

  • RipleyWolf: Exceptionally high hospital visits (115) and a significantly negative Net_Score (-432.72).
  • Blazinowl: High Drug Costs (69973500) with no war hits.
  • Happymeal: Second highest Drug Costs (3151192) with no war hits.
  • FogBorne: Very negative Net_Score (-172.51) with no war hits and high energy wasted (172.51).
  • ScatterBean: High number of hospital visits (53) and a negative Net_Score (-114.2).
  • 25mg-brenadryl: Very negative Net_Score (-202.89) and high hospital visits (41).
  • idrawfurrys: Very negative Net_Score (-187.06) and high hospital visits (32).
  • Mystic_Music: Very negative Net_Score (-209.22) and high hospital visits (40).

Additional Observations

  • Several members have high hospital visits relative to their activity and war hits, indicating potential issues with survivability or target selection.
  • Some members have zero war hits but still incurred significant energy wasted, suggesting ineffective participation or poor resource management.
  • A few members have high E_Stolen values, indicating successful defense against incoming attacks.
  • Several members have drug costs that may not be worth the war hits they contributed.
